sse_mean = function(x)
  {na.x = is.na(x)
  x2 = x[!na.x]
  sd.x2 = sd(x2)
  n = length(x2)
  sd.x2/(sqrt(n))}

two_group_resample = function(x, n_1, n_2)
{
  dat_1 = sample(x, n_1, replace = TRUE)
dat_2 = sample(x, n_2, replace = TRUE)

diff_simulated = 
  mean(dat_1, na.rm = TRUE) - mean(dat_2, na.rm = TRUE)
return(diff_simulated)
}

set.seed(54321)

sse_mean = function(x)
  {na.x = is.na(x)
  x2 = x[!na.x]
  sd.x2 = sd(x2)
  n = length(x2)
  sse = sd.x2/(sqrt(n)) 
  return(sse)
  }

two_group_resample = function(x, n_1, n_2)

  {
  dat_1 = sample(x, n_1, replace = TRUE)
dat_2 = sample(x, n_2, replace = TRUE)

diff_means = 
  mean(dat_1, na.rm = TRUE) - mean(dat_2, na.rm = TRUE)
return(diff_means)
}
